Avis Reunion Buys Franchise in Mauritius, L’Express Reports

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-03-29T08:59:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/avis-reunion-buys-franchise-in-mauritius-l-express-reports.html
Avis Reunion, a car-rental company
in the Indian Ocean island nation, bought the franchise for
 Mauritius , Port Louis-based l’Express reported on its website,
citing Anand Lutchumun, an accountant involved in the sale.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
